 drivers/net/dsa/mv88e6xxx/chip.h    |  6 +++
 drivers/net/dsa/mv88e6xxx/global1.c | 18 +++++--
 drivers/net/dsa/mv88e6xxx/port.c    | 37 ++++++++++++++
